    "This survey identified a common theme of \"course design\" that encompasses various concepts and practices.",
    "These include the following:",
    "Active Learning Practices: Many online cybersecurity courses incorporate active learning strategies to engage students and enhance their learning experience.",
    "Our research shows that approximately 11% of the articles surveyed in this study show an element of active learning practices.",
    "These practices may involve interactive exercises, group discussions, case studies, simulations, and hands-on activities that encourage active participation and application of knowledge. 2."
